Ingredient Checklist

Directions

Instructions Checklist

  • Spread 1 tablespoon chocolate-hazelnut spread on 1 half of each English muffin; arrange banana slices on top. Spread 1 tablespoon marshmallow cream on the other half. Press both halves together to create a sandwich.
